-- Access Bank of Nigeria Signs Trade Finance Accord With Africa Finance Corp
-- Vincent Nwanma
-- 2010-07-13T06:33:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/access-bank-of-nigeria-signs-trade-finance-accord-with-africa-finance-corp.html

          
          
             Access Bank Plc , a Nigerian lender,
has signed a trade finance agreement with Africa Finance Corp.,
the organization that funds infrastructure development in the
continent.  
 The accord will “provide a platform for collaboration
between the two institutions in the area of trade finance” and
open the way to further cooperation “with particular focus on
infrastructure financing,” the Lagos-based bank said in an e-
mailed statement late yesterday.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
 Vincent Nwanma  in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net .  
          
          


  


        